metadata.name: Ahiru no Omocha (MEGAMI)
metadata.description:
Ever got so pissed to the point where you want to throw someone with anything? This MEGAMI provides you a cute and deadly Rubber Duck that can send someone to the sky!!

Yes, she's the Goddess of Rubber Duck.
